305
00:17:43,780 --> 00:17:45,368
FRANK: Reach me?

306
00:17:45,370 --> 00:17:47,388
Yeah, I didn't have a current address.

307
00:17:47,390 --> 00:17:48,221
FRANK: I've lived
here in this apartment

