00:17:48,223 --> 00:17:50,198
since you were 12-years-old.

309
00:17:50,200 --> 00:17:52,488
Yeah, right, sorry.

310
00:17:52,490 --> 00:17:53,321
FRANK: Besides, I
wouldn't have been any

